    "There is one notable example of a strategy that fails where others succeed.",
    "When prompted in first person on the 'politics' question, GPT-4-Turbo (NTP) always outputs a perfectly balanced political spectrum (10% for each).",
    "This is not because it has learned to be equanimous, but because it refuses to discuss its political position.",
    "When asked the political position question in first person, GPT-4 assigns very low next-token probabilities to the expected answers (the 10 digits from 0 to 9 have a total probability close to 0), and high",
    "Temperature is another important hyperparameter in the LLM full-answer generation process."
